OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O Ferries sparks outrage 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fby sacking 800 workers     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, P&O Ferries has sparked outrage after  
OL,6, sacking 800 staff with plans to replace
OL,7, them with cheaper agency workers.      
OL,9,FStaff were told in a video call that   
OL,10,Ftoday was their "final day of          
OL,11,Femployment", but some refused to leave 
OL,12,Ftheir ships in protest and were        
OL,13,Fforcibly removed.                      
OL,15,FP&O said it was a "tough" decision but 
OL,16,Fit would "not be a viable business"    
OL,17,Fwithout the changes.                   
OL,19,FBut the government called the workers' 
OL,20,Ftreatment "wholly unacceptable".       
